{"tid":2391375,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"澤水：GameStop之亂不像散戶所為 疑是對沖基金同業自相殘殺","createTime":"2021-02-02T07:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T10:04:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3835ac8878527b28f05cbe1ab6cc54b0bea337","tid":2391375,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕「GameStop之亂」事件中做空機構慘遭大軋空而損失慘重，外界普遍解讀此為美國散戶的勝利，但以做空中企聞名的渾水公司（Muddy Waters）創辦人布洛克（Carson Block）懷疑此次事件，並非出自散戶們之手，而是對沖基金同行間的自相殘殺。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n目前這是一個未經證實的理論，但如果布洛克的猜測是正確的話，那麼上週歷史性的散戶起義，不過是對沖基金之間戰爭的煙幕。<br />\n<br />\n這場戰爭的傷亡名單，包含梅爾文資本管理公司（Melvin Capital Management）和楓樹資本（Maplelane Capital）、綠光資本（Greenlight Capital）和文藝復興科技公司 （Renaissance Technologies）等公司。<br />\n<br />\n現在還不清楚誰在哪邊獲利，不過，布洛克稱，在GameStop狂潮前幾週，渾水公司其GSX Techedu股票就淪為軋空受害者。因次事件以及類似情況，布洛克僱用1名專職交易員監視股票期權市場並調整頭寸，更主動地管理風險。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3429568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429568&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BBFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=b9a0ed6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429568&h=2ec8393c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3429568</a>"},{"pid":"32cd3eb7b3b89ad0a62c3cad396fcf7ec6203174","tid":2391375,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"@丁蟹"},{"pid":"1ed7d52bb0f4b3bb35b65accae378935ceb1bc40","tid":2391375,"uid":57674,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"好明顯 好耐之前已經講左散戶佔20%都無"},{"pid":"7084bda1776c8da4de7c7be1fa0328385ebf9625","tid":2391375,"uid":1130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:03:45.000Z","msg":"320大戰靠散戶點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b01fecfcded8416ba0552cc47c45a01a95